{"tid":2055812,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"髮型求教!!!! 想遮住一隻耳仔! because of earbud","createTime":"2020-06-08T08:40:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-08T10:31:26.000Z","uid":180069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"95c17324ffd79dde28872f30369a3b2296c4a87a","tid":2055812,"uid":180069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T08:40:54.000Z","msg":"一向都斜陰, under剷, 3mm長度<br />\n<br />\n見女同事返工聽歌好爽~<br />\n我又試下留長頭髮到遮住耳仔<br />\n咦家返工長戴住一隻Earbud聽電台<br />\n時間真係充實好多<br />\n<br />\n但真係好&quot;嬲丘&quot; 好辛苦<br />\nKeep住都係另一半幫我一邊剷<br />\n有陰果邊就Undercut剷<br />\n而面果堆就唔理佢, 一直留長<br />\n<br />\n由於無修過陰, 無剪過關係,<br />\n成堆草咁<br />\n<br />\n想入髮型屋剪, 話要遮一隻耳仔既髮型<br />\n其實有無架? 好似未見過男士剪成咁~<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n返工聽電台聽成日真係時間快過好多!!!"},{"pid":"110f049f81eba7a3725f4007c4d0378cf23391ef","tid":2055812,"uid":29080,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T08:44:12.000Z","msg":"你話剪郭炳江髮型佢就明"},{"pid":"aea4c1ccbef180f43d651a8e9c669c93edbe020f","tid":2055812,"uid":14513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T08:45:14.000Z","msg":"阿漿頭"},{"pid":"fba3d127eeb5a48ba8e008b7f9c340d224075bb2","tid":2055812,"uid":180069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"110f049f81eba7a3725f4007c4d0378cf23391ef","tid":2055812,"uid":29080,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T08:44:12.000Z","msg":"你話剪郭炳江髮型佢就明"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T09:09:16.000Z","msg":"咪撚化我啦，認真架"},{"pid":"d910ea31ec7ba7ef074536bd20deb8f839cd94d5","tid":2055812,"uid":36383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"110f049f81eba7a3725f4007c4d0378cf23391ef","tid":2055812,"uid":29080,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T08:44:12.000Z","msg":"你話剪郭炳江髮型佢就明"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T09:13:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XOxKJ0G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXOxKJ0G.jpg&h=88cfd003&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁咪兩邊遮曬